history.content:
Hey everyone! If you are interested in being an executive or project manager for Berkeley's newest Technology Consulting Club, PlexTech, apply at our website: plextech.berkeley.edu!

PlexTech teaches students to succeed in industry-related projects by aiming to enrich all Berkeley students with essential software engineering principles and connecting members to development projects from multiple Silicon Valley Companies.

Please learn more about us at our website or contact us at info@plextech.berkeley.edu with any questions!
